Health and RehabilitationProperties Trust said it reached an understanding to purchasethree nursing facilities in Mass. and Conn. for 29 mln dlrsfrom Greenery Rehabilitation Group Inc &lt;GRGI.O>.    The buildings will be leased back to Greenery for aninitial term of seven years, subject to renewal options for anadditional 23 years, Health and Rehabilitation Properties said.    The transaction is expected to close on or before August 31. Reuter&#3;